oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Nashville Songwriters Association International's Legislative Show (June 29, 2006)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Bluebird Café (Restaurant : Nashville, Tenn.); Fund raising; Lyricists;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color lobby card (green and purple on light yellow) announcing the Nashville Songwriters Association International's Legislative Show featuring hit songwriters Al Anderson, Leslie Satcher, Tim Johnson, and Will Robinson at The Bluebird Cafe on June 29. Proceeds from the event go towards NSAI's Legislative efforts, which support the rights of songwriters everywhere.
